to_lex_monotone:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
--fun_like.coe_injective
theorem to_lex_monotone : Monotone (@toLex («expr →₀ » α N)) := fun a b h =>
  Dfinsupp.toLex_monotone (id h : ∀ i, ofLex (toDfinsupp a) i ≤ ofLex (toDfinsupp b) i)
#align to_lex_monotone to_lex_monotone
lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
theorem lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt (a b : Lex («expr →₀ » α N)) (i : α) :
    (∀ j < i, ofLex a j = ofLex b j) → ofLex a i < ofLex b i → a < b := fun h1 h2 => ⟨i, h1, h2⟩
#align lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt lt_of_forall_lt_of_lt
lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
theorem lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder [preorder N] (r) [is_strict_order α r] {x y : «expr →₀ » α N} (hlt : x < y) :
    ∃ i, (∀ j, r j i → x j ≤ y j ∧ y j ≤ x j) ∧ x i < y i :=
  Dfinsupp.lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder r (id hlt : x.to_dfinsupp < y.to_dfinsupp)
#align lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder lex_lt_of_lt_of_preorder
lex_lt_of_lt:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
theorem lex_lt_of_lt [partial_order N] (r) [is_strict_order α r] {x y : «expr →₀ » α N} (hlt : x < y) :
    Pi.Lex r (fun i => (· < ·)) x y :=
  Dfinsupp.lex_lt_of_lt r (id hlt : x.to_dfinsupp < y.to_dfinsupp)
#align lex_lt_of_lt lex_lt_of_lt
lex_eq_inv_image_dfinsupp_lex:
theorem lex_eq_inv_image_dfinsupp_lex (r : α → α → Prop) (s : N → N → Prop) :
    Finsupp.Lex r s = inv_image (Dfinsupp.Lex r fun a => s) toDfinsupp :=
  rfl
#align lex_eq_inv_image_dfinsupp_lex lex_eq_inv_image_dfinsupp_lex

lex_def:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
theorem lex_def {r : α → α → Prop} {s : N → N → Prop} {a b : «expr →₀ » α N} :
    Finsupp.Lex r s a b ↔ ∃ j, (∀ d, r d j → a d = b d) ∧ s (a j) (b j) :=
  iff.rfl
#align lex_def lex_def
